      "description": "BRANCH tier (MEASURED). AP7900 single-bank amps \u2192 watts (\u00f710 \u00d7 $pdu_voltage). NOT summed with WALL \u2014 this bank sits under one UPS and is already inside its WALL total.",
      "datasource": {
